@{"b"}Amiga Hardware List@{"ub"}  

This is a new section where I list some of the latest and best Amiga products available, with brief descriptions, contacts and prices (correct as of sometime June/July '97)  

 
    	
    @{"b"}Amigas!@{"ub"}  
    
    @{"b"}A1200 'Magic' Pack@{"ub"} - Same as always, but check out First's new hardware bundles! (First Computer Centre, £299.99) 
    @{"b"}Eagle A1200TE@{"ub"} - Tower based A1200s, with 40MHz '040 or 50MHz '060 (?, £700/£900) 
    @{"b"}Direct's Power Amiga@{"ub"} - £1499, Direct 'Software'. Looks a great machine, can't wait for the PPC version! 
    
    	
    @{"b"}Accelerators@{"ub"}  
    
    @{"b"}Viper 630@{"ub"} - New range of '030 accelerators for the A600 (Power, £100-£130) 
    @{"b"}Viper MkIV@{"ub"} - 42MHz '030 for A1200 with 4MB RAM (unexpandable) for just £89.95! (Power) 
    @{"b"}Viper MkV@{"ub"} - 50MHz '030 for A1200 with built in SCSI-2! (Power, £139.95) 
    @{"b"}Blizzard 1230@{"ub"} - 50MHz '030 for A1200 (Harwoods,  £99.95) 
    @{"b"}Blizzard 1260@{"ub"} - 50MHz '060 for A1200 (Blittersoft, £329.95) 
    @{"b"}Blizzard PPC 603e@{"ub"} - 603e PowerUP board (I think at 180MHz). Requires '030 CPU. (Blittersoft, £299.95(!) ) 
    @{"b"}Cyberstorm II@{"ub"} - 40MHz '040 or 50MHz '060 for A3000/A4000. Upgradeable to PPC. (Harwoods, £319.95/£479.95) 
    @{"b"}Cyberstorm PPC 604e@{"ub"} 604e PowerUP board, either 150MHz, 180MHz, 200MHz (Blittersoft, 150MHz-£479.95/200MHz-£679.95) 
    
    	
    @{"b"}Graphics Cards@{"ub"}  
    
    @{"b"}Picasso IV@{"ub"} - 4MB 64bit graphics card, generally regarded as better than the Cybervision (Blittersoft, £299.95) 
    @{"b"}Cybervision 64/3D@{"ub"} - Another card (Harwoods, £199.95, £84.95 for Monitor Switcher) 
    Picasso II+@{"ub"} - Older card (Blittersoft, £199.95) 
    
    	
    @{"b"}CD ROM Drives@{"ub"}  
    
    @{"b"}Power CD ROMs@{"ub"} - External SCSI drives, with free squirrel i/face. 2x, 4x or 12x. (Power, £99.95/£139.95/£229.95) 
    @{"b"}Ultra CD ROM@{"ub"} - External 6x IDE drive for A1200 (First, £159.99)     
 
 
